Our
team

FairlieExintaris

The founder of Miss Luxe, Fairlie has spent many years perfecting the art of brows and has extensive experience in bridal, editorial and commercial makeup. Fairlie also specialises in feather touch brows, her style being a soft, natural and well balanced semi-permanent brow. Regularly attending master classes, work shops and seminars She is constantly building on her skills to remain ahead in her field and counts many well known Australian and internationally recognised faces among her loyal followers.

Gabby

Gabby has moved to Australia from the U.S. where she built her skills as a makeup artist attending classes with celebrity makeup artists including Mario Dedivanovic, (best know for his work with Kim Kardashian), assisting a well know makeup artist in New York City and working as an assistant on Project Runway. Gabby's appreciation and understanding of amazing brows has lead her to train under Fairlie at Miss Luxe perfecting her brow and lash styling skills. Gabby is the master of beautiful, full brows.
